text: Laura Anne Gillen (born July 10, 1969) is an American politician and attorney who is the member of the United States House of Representatives for New York's 4th congressional district since 2025. She is a Democrat. She was the town supervisor of Hempstead, New York from 2018 to 2019. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from New York (state) Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Lawyers from New York (state) Category:People from Rockville Centre, New York
